  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose will be to study the functional impact of pediatric chronic pain on children, and
      their families. Focus will be on the impact of pain on school functioning, social
      functioning, psychological functioning and family functioning of pediatric chronic pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
